text: Laura Magitteri (born 30 December 1988) is an Italian former pair skater. She teamed up with Ondřej Hotárek in January 2006. Two-time (2007–08) Italian national champions, they placed as high as ninth at the European Championships (2007), 13th at the World Championships (2008), and competed at three Grand Prix events.
